Setup wlan1 on boot

Fetch github on boot
Setup autostart for barndoor and barnshed (pm2 on boot with good names)

Setup full hardware stack
Setup api to convert hold position to led position

Setup conf file for prod and dev urls


for it to work:
git fetch
git reset origin/main --hard
cp barndoor .next/static to /var/www/barndoor/static
cp .env to .next/standalone/

be sure pm2 runs for both apps, be sure mongo runs


Setup auto build on commit/push and add .next/standalone and .next/static
Rename raspberrypi.local to barnboard.local